expression: left join ccb_mtr_char mc on m.mtr_id = mc.mtr_id
join ccb_mtr_config mcf on mcf.mtr_id = m.mtr_id
join ccb_sp_mtr_hist_refined smh on smh.mtr_config_id = mcf.mtr_config_id
join ccb_sa_sp_fa ss on ss.sp_id = smh.sp_id
join ccb_sa sa on sa.sa_id = ss.sa_id
lag(record_type_cd) over (partition by control_no order by sys_identified_batch_dt) as previous_record_type_cd,
lag(field_elig_cd) over (partition by control_no order by sys_identified_batch_dt) as previous_field_elig_cd
where previous_record_type_cd <> record_type_cd or previous_field_elig_cd <> field_elig_cd or previous_record_type_cd is null
join delta_hub.ccb_sa_sp_fa ssf on fa.fa_id = ssf.fa_id
join delta_hub.ccb_sa sa on sa.sa_id = ssf.sa_id
where sa._curr_record is true and ssf._curr_record is true
join acct_mtrs am on fa.fa_id = am.fa_id
and (retire_dt is null or retire_dt > fa_completion_dt)
and (removal_dttm is null or removal_dttm > fa_completion_dt)
first_value(fa_type_cd) over (partition by control_no order by fa_completion_dt) first_fa_type
join ranked_ccb_fa fa on f.control_no = fa.control_no
join combined_base b on a.control_no = b.control_no and a.record_type_cd = b.record_type_cd
and a.field_elig_cd = b.field_elig_cd and a.sys_identified_batch_dt = b.sys_identified_batch_dt
coalesce(lead(sys_identified_batch_dt) over (partition by control_no order by sys_identified_batch_dt), '2999-12-31') as record_end_dt
lag(record_type_cd) over (partition by control_no order by sys_identified_batch_dt) as previous_record_type_cd,
lag(field_elig_cd) over (partition by control_no order by sys_identified_batch_dt) as previous_field_elig_cd
when previous_record_type_cd is null and sys_identified_batch_dt > doc_recd_dt then date_add(sys_identified_batch_dt, -1)
row_number() over (partition by acct_id, to_date(field_start_dttm) order by case when field_action = 'Payment' then 1 when field_action = 'TONP' then 2 else 3 end) as rn
-- joining in field visits that happened either on or the day before a doc status change
left join jobs_reached b on a.control_no = b.control_no
when previous_record_type_cd is null and record_type_cd = 'A' and field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'In' -- Newly Fieldable

when field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_start_dt > doc_recd_dt then 'In' -- Non-Fieldable to Fieldable

when previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'Out' -- Active Fieldable to Non-Fieldable
when previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and record_type_cd <> 'A' then 'Out' -- Active Fieldable to Non-Active
when fa_type_cd = 'POST-MLT' and record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_record_type_cd is null then 'MDAC Pending Postering'
when fa_type_cd = 'POST-MLT' and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and record_type_cd <> 'A' then 'MDAC Public Notice Posted'
when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-DOC' and record_start_dt = doc_recd_dt and field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'Newly Fieldable Document'
when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-CWI' and record_start_dt = doc_recd_dt and field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'New CWI'

when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-DOC' and field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_start_dt > doc_recd_dt then 'Activated Document'

when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-CWI' and field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and record_start_dt > doc_recd_dt then 'Activated CWI'
when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-DOC' and field_dt is not null
and ((previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N'))
or (previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and record_type_cd <> 'A')) then 'Document Resolved in Field'

when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-DOC' and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'Inactive Document'

when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-CWI' and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and field_elig_cd not in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') then 'Inactive CWI'
when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-DOC' and previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and record_type_cd <> 'A' then 'Closed Document'
when fa_type_cd = 'COLL-CWI' and previous_field_elig_cd in ('1','4','6','E','G','H','J','K','L','N') and previous_record_type_cd = 'A' and record_type_cd <> 'A' then 'Closed CWI'
